--- !u!114 &114680922687545197
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInternal: {fileID: 100100000}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 1709254077376921}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 56ec6c25ac577afeb80be7acb7b0702d, type: 3}
  m_Name:
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  tutorials:
  - logs:
    - content_en: "Welcome to SCP: Secret Laboratory! I'm one of the voice actors for the game.\nLet me introduce you to basic gameplay rules.\nTry to find and check toilets in order to find a potential keycard.\n"
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 99e601a240e7ca0479284578d7e8b456, type: 3}
      duration_en: 12
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias:
    - content_en: "<color=#00FF58>Use <b>W, A, S & D</b> in order to go to the <b>toilets</b>\nUse <b>E</b> to <b>interact</b> with doors and items.</color>"
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: 10000
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Great, now take it.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5c916043b7f907e4bad48c671bcc1354, type: 3}
      duration_en: 2
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: "Keycards are one of the most basic elements of the game, allowing entrance to locked areas.\nCheck the nearby doors and try to open them with your card."
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 5845f4fb88c8d314f912342b4f8d85d8, type: 3}
      duration_en: 8
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: scientist
    - content_en: "<color=#00FF58>Use <b>TAB</b> to open inventory.\r\n<b>Left mouse button</b> to select item\r\nand <b>right</b> to drop it."
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: 10000
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: If you really want to escape - I'd suggest finding a better card.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 54455bcc2b0d04c49bcdc7ceb5f91323, type: 3}
      duration_en: 4
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: better
    - content_en: Every card has its own access levels. You can compare cards by hovering your mouse cursor over each one in your inventory.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 62bd139a89de9d04e83793f329ddfe07, type: 3}
      duration_en: 7
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: manager
    - content_en: Congratulations! You just passed the first part of the tutorial!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: e099e2d5f2728f1409b04d585c9db375, type: 3}
      duration_en: 4
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias: finish
    - content_en:
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -100
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias:
  - logs:
    - content_en: "Ok, let's get started...\nLearning the basics skills of shooting definitely makes gameplay... <i>easier</i>.\nPick Up the pistol that just landed on the board."
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: d6e05c6fe26de0442a67a8a5dc9bc83e, type: 3}
      duration_en: 11
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Curtain
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: pistoltake
    - content_en: So, you just picked up the shittiest weapon in the game. Get used to it, because it'll get you out of some pretty hairy situations. Oh, and it's good to have some ammunition. It is difficult to find it in the game, so shoot as efficiently as you can.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9d7a9622a409a7c4ebf8673bf49fbf50, type: 3}
      duration_en: 14
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_GiveAmmo
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Remember, that headshots will take down your opponent faster. If you run out of ammo in this test, I'll give you more!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 26e353c8bc3bc7e498055dfda50e16c2, type: 3}
      duration_en: 6.5
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: "<color=#00FF58>Use <b>R</b> to reload,\n<b>right mouse button</b> to zoom\nand <b>left</b> to shoot.</color>"
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: 10000
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: keybinding
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Result
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Impressive, you dispatched them all with a single magazine!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8e8ea6a62ce9e304e9602b6ad0669f0a, type: 3}
      duration_en: 4
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: result_good
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Jumpin
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Hey, you're pretty good at shooting!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9900967d4213bb94d914a77ccd330216, type: 3}
      duration_en: 2
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: result_ok
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Jumpin
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: I really hoped for a bigger display of skill, such a shame.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2491129431b7bde468bc26a446a06e36, type: 3}
      duration_en: 6
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: result_bad
    - content_en: Tutorial2_GiveNTFRifle
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: epsilon
    - content_en: "Ok, I hope you hate this weapon as much as I do, let's put the toys a side, and pick up a real weapon. This one has an night vision sight that makes shooting easier.\r\nYou should know, that zooming or aiming any weapon guarantees accuracy and a greater reduction of recoil."
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 831be9f94ab2a1349a9a82565c344efc, type: 3}
      duration_en: 17
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Preset
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Curtain
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Curtain
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: secondkill
    - content_en: "I can see you've already mastered the basics! I have prepared a challenge for you.\nYou have 20 seconds to kill as many opponents as you can.\nLet's get started!"
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 90dfd83c512cf00458e5acbd25598d3d, type: 3}
      duration_en: 11
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Ready? 3, 2, 1... GO
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 2676b4aaa5c02614d89867df9de30a09, type: 3}
      duration_en: 5
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Preset
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Curtain
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en:
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 09108b8a0c25a3145848b61832e5c6ee, type: 3}
      duration_en: 20
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_ResultText
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_Curtain
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Time's up!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 4f13c151e9f198947b905e7914bd0596, type: 3}
      duration_en: 1
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: "Remember that you can always re-visit this tutorial in the future\nif you want to brush up on your skills!\nSee you later!"
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 97a6347417f777346b87e52acfe4298a, type: 3}
      duration_en: 8
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en:
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -100
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial2_MoreAmmo
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: ammoplz
  - logs:
    - content_en: Here we go! There is no round in which you won't have to use SCP-914. It's a special machine that allows you to change the access level of your keycards. Please enter the containment chamber.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c16681ac859e9f6489313dd81a36a87b, type: 3}
      duration_en: 12
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias:
    - content_en: Look at the panel with the knob. It can be turned into 5 different positions.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 16cd0b2aceb1b774a9637aedb5ccebd3, type: 3}
      duration_en: 6
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: "1:1 - changes the type of a keycard. For instance:\nthe Scientist keycard to a Guard keycard;\nor an MTF commander keycard to a Containment engineer keycard"
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9f1154bb2c7c0f84c823df2d8f17bbc8, type: 3}
      duration_en: 13.5
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Fine - increases the level of the card, and Coarse - decreases it.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 573c8e64a9c2d234b996ee48cf03ff45, type: 3}
      duration_en: 6
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Very fine and Rough are equivalents of Fine and Coarse. They're faster, but more risky.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 1bab217dab9e73f4289ac265a0b87b37, type: 3}
      duration_en: 7
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Tutorial3_GiveKeycard
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: "I just threw you a card somewhere on the floor.\nPick it up and try to upgrade it to the highest level - the O5 Keycard."
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: f1e313e495c5fa447af29095bec79274, type: 3}
      duration_en: 8
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: '<color=#00FF58>Set the knob to <b>Fine, Very fine or 1:1</b> to upgrade the keycard.'
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: 10
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: What have you done? I didn't expect this... there's nothing interesting, go back to SCP-914!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 15bad3ce61328494ea41935018c3b9e9, type: 3}
      duration_en: 8
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: armory
    - content_en: You did something wrong and you burned it. No problem, take another one.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 03e36c2c175ef514da1fc5c51b9d946d, type: 3}
      duration_en: 6
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: bc1
    - content_en: Oh, you did it again! Come on! Take the next one.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 71d1e50aae261bf42a83256cf1fb2487, type: 3}
      duration_en: 7
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: bc2
    - content_en: "You know what? Maybe I will give you 5 keycards for once?\nRemember, we want O5-level keycard, no ash."
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 909379e80c0072744a3e8963489fb3f1, type: 3}
      duration_en: 9.5
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: bc3
    - content_en: Ehh, you are doing it on purpose. Do you think this is funny? You know what I can do, and you can't prevent? Quitting the game! Yeah! Come back later when you a little smarter!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 9255b5e4bc812884aab081af65c6a004, type: 3}
      duration_en: 14
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias: bc4
    - content_en: Tutorial3_Quit
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -200
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
    - content_en: Well done! With this card can enter anywhere! I see that you understand what SCP-914 is. I hope you will be able to use the acquired skills in normal gameplay. Good luck!
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 964097c8f04f48848bbca1f2019e4ef4, type: 3}
      duration_en: 14
      jumpforward: 1
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias: complete
    - content_en:
      clip_en: {fileID: 0}
      duration_en: -100
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 0
      alias:
  - logs:
    - content_en: Here we go! There is no round in which you won't have to use SCP-914. It's a special machine that allows you to change the access level of your keycards. Please enter the containment chamber.
      clip_en: {fileID: 8300000, guid: c16681ac859e9f6489313dd81a36a87b, type: 3}
      duration_en: 12
      jumpforward: 0
      stopPlayer: 1
      alias:
